# 08 - Meeting Notes Processor
# Transform raw notes into actionable summaries

NAME meeting-processor
INPUT notes_file

GOAL read_notes "Read meeting notes from $notes_file."
GOAL extract "Extract: decisions (max 5), action items with owners, open questions. Skip redundant discussion."
GOAL format "Format as: Summary (2-3 sentences), Decisions, Action Items, Open Questions."
GOAL save "Write to file with '-processed' suffix."

RUN process USING read_notes, extract, format, save
